      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Afton%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Afton once served as a hidden station on the Underground Railroad, aiding escaping slaves.",
